      </math>) = $200.</dd>
    <dd>Number of payments (n) =20. Unit-period = 2 months.</dd>
    <dd>Unit-periods per year (w) = 12/2 = 6.</dd>
    <dd>Advance, 1-10-78. First payment, 3-1-78.</dd>
    <dd>From 2-1-78 through 3-1-78 = 1 month. From 1-10-78</dd>
    <dd>through 2-1-78 = 22 days. (t = 0; f = 52/60)</dd>
    <dd>Annual percentage rate (I) = wi = .0730 = 7.30%</dd>
